properties.areaDesc: Manitou Island to Point Isabelle MI; Eagle River to Manitou Island MI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 13 at 4:19PM EST until January 14 at 7:00PM EST by NWS Marquette MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...South winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and
waves 3 to 6 feet expected.

* WHERE...Eagle River to Manitou Island MI and Manitou Island to
Point Isabelle MI.

* WHEN...From 11 PM this evening to 7 PM EST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 11 PM THIS EVENING TO 7 PM EST TUESDAY
